{"id": "optoppen-blijft-steken-in-belofte-slechts-7-procent-van-potentieel-benut__c4-paragraph__0020", "text": "The Dutch construction sector has been one of the best performing sectors in recent years, despite several challenges facing the sector. Examples are the nitrogen dossier, the significant price increases for energy and building materials and also the personnel shortages. Driven by trends, innovations and legislation and regulations, the relevance of themes such as sustainability and environmental impact is growing and the sector is looking for a new balance.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "optoppen-blijft-steken-in-belofte-slechts-7-procent-van-potentieel-benut__c4-paragraph__0020", "source_slug": "optoppen-blijft-steken-in-belofte-slechts-7-procent-van-potentieel-benut", "source_title": "Topping remains stuck in promise; only 7 percent of potential is utilised", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/optoppen-blijft-steken-in-belofte-slechts-7-procent-van-potentieel-benut.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 20, "n_chunks_total": 35, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
